},[299,771,412],{"class":333},[299,773,775,777],{"class":301,"line":774},13,[299,776,418],{"class":333},[299,778,421],{"class":329},[277,780,782],{"id":781},"_2-部署你的项目","2. 部署你的项目",[240,784,785],{},"Nuxt Content 使用 Nuxt 部署预设来调整不同托管平台的构建流程。",[240,787,788],{},"以下无服务器平台支持零配置：",[257,790,791,799,805,811],{},[260,792,793],{},[263,794,798],{"href":795,"rel":796},"https://nuxt.com/deploy/cloudflare",[797],"nofollow","Cloudflare",[260,800,801],{},[263,802,124],{"href":803,"rel":804},"https://nuxt.com/deploy/nuxthub",[797],[260,806,807],{},[263,808,136],{"href":809,"rel":810},"https://nuxt.com/deploy/vercel",[797],[260,812,813],{},[263,814,140],{"href":815,"rel":816},"https://nuxt.com/deploy/netlify",[797],[240,818,819],{},"你只需将构建命令设置为：",[288,821,826],{"className":822,"code":823,"filename":824,"language":825,"meta":294,"style":294},"language-bash shiki shiki-themes material-theme-lighter material-theme material-theme-palenight","nuxi build\n","Terminal","bash",[296,827,828],{"__ignoreMap":294},[299,829,830,834],{"class":301,"line":302},[299,831,833],{"class":832},"sBMFI","nuxi",[299,835,836],{"class":371}," build\n",[240,838,839],{},"生成的输出将兼容所选平台。",[841,842,843],"note",{},[240,844,845,846,850],{},"链接的数据库将在服务器启动时于服务器端加载。浏览器端将加载一个 ",[263,847,849],{"href":848},"/docs/advanced/database#wasm-sqlite-in-browser","WASM SQLite"," 数据库，用于客户端导航和操作。",[852,853,854,861],"tip",{},[240,855,856,857,860],{},"如果你想部署到 AWS Lambda 或 Azure Static Web Apps，你需要确保你的 sqlite 文件在 ",[296,858,859],{},"/tmp"," 目录下，因为这是唯一可写的文件夹。",[288,862,864],{"className":290,"code":863,"language":293,"meta":294,"style":294},"export default defineNuxtConfig({\n  modules: ['@nuxt/content'],\n  content: {\n    database: {\n      type: 'sqlite',\n      filename: '/tmp/contents.sqlite'\n    }\n  }\n})\n",[296,865,866,878,896,904,912,927,941,945,949],{"__ignoreMap":294},[299,867,868,870,872,874,876],{"class":301,"line":302},[299,869,319],{"class":318},[299,871,322],{"class":318},[299,873,326],{"class":325},[299,875,330],{"class":